# Accounts

## [Tarantool]

IMAPStore tarantool-remote
Host imap.mail.ru
User m.shishatskiy@tarantool.org
PassCmd "pass show tarantool/m.shishatskiy@tarantool.org"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore tarantool-local
Path /mnt/WorkDisk/share/mail/tarantool/
Inbox /mnt/WorkDisk/share/mail/tarantool/inbox/

Channel tarantool-inbox
Far :tarantool-remote:"INBOX"
Near :tarantool-local:inbox
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel tarantool-sent
Far :tarantool-remote:"Отправленные"
Near :tarantool-local:sent
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel tarantool-drafts
Far :tarantool-remote:"Черновики"
Near :tarantool-local:drafts
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel tarantool-spam
Far :tarantool-remote:"Спам"
Near :tarantool-local:spam
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel tarantool-trash
Far :tarantool-remote:"Корзина"
Near :tarantool-local:trash
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Group tarantool
Channel tarantool-inbox
Channel tarantool-sent
Channel tarantool-drafts
Channel tarantool-spam
Channel tarantool-trash

## [Ispras]

IMAPStore ispras-remote
Host mail.ispras.ru
User shishqa@ispras.ru
PassCmd "pass show ispras/mail"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

